# Group PlatformVersions
PlatformVersions can be accessed here, and admins can update / add new ones.

## PlatformVersions Collection [/platformVersions?limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `platform`, or `all`

