## PlatformVersion [/platformVersions/id?include=includes]
Get a single PlatformVersion object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Note to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `platform`, or `all`

### Retrieve a PlatformVersion [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                data: {
                  modified_by: null
                  platform_version: 2.2 
                  platform_id: 2
                  created_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                  updated_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                  class: "PlatformVersion"
                  version: 1
                  modifier: null
                  id: 2
                }
            }

